    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "SAN FRANCISCO,\nOAKLAND\nUNITED\nNEW, EASY-REFERENCE\nCITY TIMETABLE\nSEPTEMBER 24, 1961",
      "VANCOUVER\nSEATTLE TACOMA\nSPOKANE\nPOKELANL\nEUGENE\nMEDFORD\nMINNEAPONS STE PAUL\nSAGINAW BAY CITY MIDLAND\nCEDAR KA:\nMULINE/ROCK ISLAND/DAVENPORT DAYTON\nSAN FRANGIOGU\nOAKLAND\nMONTEREY\nSANTA BARBARA\nSALT LAKE CITY\nGRAND JUNCTION\nCOLUMBU\nPROVIDENCE\nWEWARK\nN/BETHLCHEM /LASTON\nHIT ADEI PHIA\nALTIMORE\nYASHING ON\nNEWPORT NEWS\nHAMPTON /WILLIAMSBURG\nNORFOLK PORTSMOUTH\n/ISALIA\nBAKERSFIELU\nSON CITY /KINGSPORT\nGREENSBUKU\nASHEVILLE/HENDERS\nCHAITANUUGA\nSAN DIEGO\nBIRMINGHAM\nNEW ORLEANS\nST. PETERSBURG\nUnited flights are timed to the stars by the Elgin National Watch Company.\nUNITED'S RED CARPET SERVICE\n... designed for discriminating travelers\n.. offering the utmost in travel luxury."
